        <q>After Clause 104, insert the following new clause&#x2014;</q>
        <q><span class="bold">"INTERNATIONAL OBLIGATIONS ON CLIMATE CHANGE AND SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT</span>
        <ol>
