        <span class="bold">OFFSETTING REPAYMENTS AGAINST</p><p> SHORTFALLS IN PAYMENTS DUE IN DISCHARGE OF</p><p> RENEWABLES OBLIGATION</span>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-06297'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040212_GCR_68' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
